ABOUT Taylor

A little bit about me.

Originally born in Michigan, I moved south to Florida after university to pursue my goals, driven by my open-mindedness and constant pursuit of the next best thing. I’ve always had a passion for music, travel, and philosophy. I’m most notable for my attention to detail and my ability to see the big picture while managing the finer aspects of any project.
